{"tid":717501,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求救，屋企條豬仔魚係咪就死","createTime":"2018-06-26T05:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T18:49:43.000Z","uid":84409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1fdfdbf6a4fbf457dce745cbe21771bb7feb64d1","tid":717501,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是咁的， 大概兩三個月前開始養左2條豬仔魚<br />\n兩條友不嬲都會打下交，但都無咩事<br />\n前排好忙無咩留意佢地個樣，今日一睇，<br />\n其中一條個身有好多白色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD 鰭又俾人打到爛哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問佢係咪病左，就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪應該再分開佢地養<br />\n<br />\n利申：養魚白痴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢哋以前係一樣色<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/133028_c98a8df5508b943352f224e04335a49b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F133028_c98a8df5508b943352f224e04335a49b.png&h=8124e65f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日其中一條個頭有白色<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/133122_cdfac4baae4b39388f76e4c9e7580471.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F133122_cdfac4baae4b39388f76e4c9e7580471.png&h=d868be48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日個身就變左咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/133222_1f3e7890c5c1c7145f9d7c6e854a34e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F133222_1f3e7890c5c1c7145f9d7c6e854a34e8.png&h=ece17904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/133312_7233b77eef09489f2ad6e6d65c78705e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F133312_7233b77eef09489f2ad6e6d65c78705e.png&h=26bb8fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/133422_0cef566e9a59ce3f55d322f5b066a8ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F133422_0cef566e9a59ce3f55d322f5b066a8ad.png&h=33d13867&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/133423_33b5a7dd5884c2526603e7be36acf4a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F133423_33b5a7dd5884c2526603e7be36acf4a2.png&h=5c300611&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/133425_a974e2564211ea6db7c9913d8da08f01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F133425_a974e2564211ea6db7c9913d8da08f01.png&h=48ca3f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有白色 又爛哂d鰭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪分開佢地就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a7235dd9e143ede3e0f654d19e33a64a9890b4","tid":717501,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"買d藥水，開盤新水加落去，再放條魚落去"},{"pid":"4e47233d5f7c16704ad0c8f4be41dcd49e0e67b4","tid":717501,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T06:54:33.000Z","msg":"如果係其中一條魚病<br />\n係咪應該兩條隔開咗先<br />\n費事感染埋另一條魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：無養魚"},{"pid":"fb47a7224a4900b41a4352cdb634157818f72281","tid":717501,"uid":133319,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T